#. <section class="sutta" id="sn17.12"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn17.12:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 17"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 17"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.12:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga"
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn17.12:0.3"
msgid "12. Rūpiyapātisutta"
msgstr "12. A Silver Bowl"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn17.12:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn17.12:1.2"
msgid "“Dāruṇo, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe …"
msgstr "“Possessions, honor, and popularity are brutal …"

msgctxt "sn17.12:1.3"
msgid "idhāhaṃ, bhikkhave, ekaccaṃ puggalaṃ evaṃ cetasā ceto paricca pajānāmi:"
msgstr "When I’ve comprehended the mind of a certain person, I understand:"

msgctxt "sn17.12:1.4"
msgid ""
"‘na cāyamāyasmā rūpiyapātiyāpi suvaṇṇacuṇṇaparipūrāya hetu sampajānamusā "
"bhāseyyā’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘This venerable would not tell a deliberate lie even for the sake of a "
"silver bowl filled with gold powder.’"

msgctxt "sn17.12:1.5"
msgid ""
"Tamenaṃ passāmi aparena samayena lābhasakkārasilokena abhibhūtaṃ "
"pariyādiṇṇacittaṃ sampajānamusā bhāsantaṃ."
msgstr ""
"But some time later I see them tell a deliberate lie because their mind is "
"overcome and overwhelmed by possessions, honor, and popularity."

msgctxt "sn17.12:1.6"
msgid "Evaṃ dāruṇo kho, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe …"
msgstr "So brutal are possessions, honor, and popularity. …”"

msgctxt "sn17.12:1.7"
msgid "evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn17.12:1.8"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
